There is no sweeter sound than the crumbling of ones fellow man=2E
To bear is to conquer our fate=2E
Nothing is more fairly distributed than common sense: no one thinks he n= eeds more of it than he already has=2E
Wisdom becomes nonsense in the mouth of a fanatic=2E
Luck can be assisted=2E It is not all chance with the wise=2E
A man who gives his children habits of industry provides for them better= than by giving them a fortune=2E
Words are the most powerful drugs used by mankind=2E
All farewells should be sudden, when forever=2E
Everyone has 20/20 hindsight
The hardest work of all is to do nothing=2E
Our faith in the present dies out long before our faith in the future=2E=
Don't waste your time striving for perfection, instead, strive for excel= lence -- doing your best=2E

There is no sweeter sound than the crumbling of ones fellow man=2E
To bear is to conquer our fate=2E
Nothing is more fairly distributed than common sense: no one thinks he n= eeds more of it than he already has=2E
Wisdom becomes nonsense in the mouth of a fanatic=2E
